snippet.title: Take the Throne - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
TAKE THE THRONE IS OUT NOW, DOWNLOAD FOR FREE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1914570/Take_the_Throne/

Take the Throne is a free new Massive Multiplayer Online Battle Royale game with up to 30 players in a free-for-all bloody fight to be crowned and take the throne! Take the Throne is built on PvP encounters and is filled with comedic physics-based gameplay.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/take_throne
Discord: http://discord.gg/4aZHrFCad9
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1914570/Take_the_Throne/
